 ('72', '4', '2', '75', 'en_us', '18', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Airbnb\",\"slug\":\"airbnb\",\"postDate\":1502508000,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"#fa3517\",\"4\":\"<p><strong>The campaign that <em>\\u201c<\\/em><em>brought the house down<\\/em><em>\\u201d<\\/em>&nbsp;at <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/bokeh.agency\\/projects\\/airbnb#entry:4:url\\\">Airbnb<\\/a>.<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"8\":\"center\",\"3\":[\"182\"],\"5\":\"On November 17, 2016, Airbnb announced the largest product expansion in its history. Just five weeks earlier, Bokeh was asked to join its sprint to the finish line.\",\"10\":{\"146\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"\\u201cThis film brought the house down. I cannot imagine now having done this without it.\\u201d\",\"avatar\":[\"73\"],\"personsName\":\"Brian Chesky\",\"jobTitle\":\"CEO of Airbnb\"}},\"147\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>Mission:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>On November 17, 2016, Airbnb announced the largest product expansion in its history. Just five weeks earlier, Bokeh was asked to join its sprint to the finish line.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Working alongside engineering, brand, product marketing, art, and C-level teams, we developed a dizzying amount of content to educate users on new features, advertise and build awareness on social media, and, ultimately, to introduce the world to Airbnb Trips on-stage at Airbnb Open in Los Angeles.<\\/p>\"}},\"153\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193175968\",\"caption\":\"Welcome to the World of Trips | Aired During Airbnb Open 2016 Keynote\"}},\"154\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"quote\":\"Services:\",\"avatar\":[\"5\"],\"personsName\":\"Services: Concept, Branding (motion logomark) Film\\/Video, Animation, Digital Ads, Social Ads\",\"jobTitle\":\"\"}},\"148\":{\"type\":\"quote\",\"enabled\":\"1\"