go<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"178\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/231786676\",\"caption\":\"Airbnb motion logo\"}},\"155\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>Let\\u2019s get functional<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We started by developing eight animated and live-action product marketing videos to introduce users to key features built into the new Airbnb app. Each video needed to be playable in both landscape and portrait mode. Double the work&hellip; double the fun.<\\/p>\"}},\"157\":{\"type\":\"videoCarousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":{\"158\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177317\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Experiences\"}},\"159\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177901\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Itinerary\"}},\"160\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177150\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Co-hosting\"}},\"161\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"video\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193177011\",\"caption\":\"Introducing Social Impact Experiences\"}}}}},\"162\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><strong>Our <\\/strong><strong><em>Argo<\\/em><\\/strong><strong> moment<\\/strong><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Meanwhile, Bokeh\\u2019s CEO, David, went undercover with an exuberant crew of filmmakers to old Havana, Cuba. With no time to obtain permits, we developed alibis to explain the excessive amount of camera gear. We got the greenlight thanks to some quick thinking and charming Spanglish. <\\/p>\"}},\"163\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/193176889\",\"caption\":\"Staying Connected in Cuba\"}},\"252\":{\"type\":\"twoUpImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"firstImage\":[\"29\"],\"secondImage\":[\"203\"]}},\"164\":{\"type\":\"threeUpImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"firstImage\":[\"152\"],\"secondI