ss than three weeks<\\/strong>. On Airbnb product pages, the <strong>video click-through-rate reached as high as 15 percent<\\/strong>. <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We received coverage in the <strong><em>NYTimes<\\/em><\\/strong><strong>, Adweek, <\\/strong><strong><em>Travel + Leisure<\\/em><\\/strong><strong>, TechCrunch, Mashable, <\\/strong><strong><em>The Telegraph<\\/em><\\/strong><strong>, and Fast Company.<\\/strong><\\/p>\"}}},\"2\":[\"96\"],\"9\":\"center\"}}', '2017-09-26 01:23:20', '2017-09-26 01:23:20', 'c7f0959f-57c5-49d2-9980-df25131aab31'),
