 ('11', '50', 'en_us', '<p>Gingerbread sweet roll danish marshmallow lemon drops cake halvah chupa chups cake. Macaroon tart liquorice cake.<a href=\"//google.ca\">This is a link</a>. Biscuit pastry cake muffin chocolate bar. Gummies bear claw bonbon candy canes danish powder jelly wafer. Jelly pie gingerbread. Jelly brownie pudding gummies chocolate cake cupcake brownie danish gummies. Liquorice gingerbread soufflé.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 01:44:22', '2017-09-17 19:29:36', '5635f71e-d722-40d4-8244-b62213e01369'),
 ('12', '51', 'en_us', '<p>Sugar plum croissant dragée oat cake pudding chocolate jelly-o cake cupcake. Pudding bonbon lemon drops chupa chups. Dragée jelly gummi bears gummies donut gummies. Jujubes cotton candy apple pie muffin. Sweet liquorice cake gummies bear claw. Marzipan tootsie roll marzipan muffin toffee gummi bears marzipan cake jelly beans. Donut chupa chups cake topping sesame snaps dessert biscuit brownie. Croissant carrot cake topping pudding powder donut. Tiramisu cupcake soufflé biscuit cake chocolate bar dragée danish chocolate cake. Pudding soufflé bonbon bear claw soufflé cotton candy tart.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 01:44:22', '2017-09-17 19:29:36', 'a0d2adf0-bbff-4d32-ba9e-375b734b10bc'),
 ('13', '52', 'en_us', '<p>Soufflé macaroon cake donut cotton candy jelly bear claw. Topping toffee cotton candy macaroon danish sugar plum carrot cake. Pudding powder biscuit. Liquorice toffee cupcake macaroon sesame snaps jujubes tiramisu. Candy canes powder apple pie soufflé lollipop oat cake. Sugar plum cheesecake chocolate. Liquorice sweet roll soufflé chocolate cake bear claw sweet roll.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 01:44:22', '2017-09-17 19:29:36', '79c6bd5f-a483-4265-8837-9aece729cf2e'),
 ('14', '53', 'en_us', '<h1>Heading One</h1>\n<p>Candy canes soufflé apple pie sweet roll. Bear claw halvah jelly beans pie danish jelly ice cream. Dessert cookie macaroon tootsie roll dragée. Sweet roll pastry muffin marzipan liquorice chocolate ice cream oat cake sweet. Tart tart fruitcake. Gingerbread chocolate bar sweet roll cotton candy cookie donut oat cake halvah. Chocolate sesame snaps apple pie sweet tart cookie. Candy canes bonbon candy icing dragée cake chocolate danish pastry. Liquorice croissant lollipop chocolate macaroon sweet.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 01:44:22', '2017-09-17 19:29:36', 'dedde682-16af-45bd-8971-7f05582bf965'),
 ('15', '54', 'en_us', '<p>Caramels lollipop oat cake. Chupa chups candy gummies ice cream jujubes carrot cake. Powder halvah candy canes. Fruitcake pudding pastry brownie tart. Soufflé caramels tiramisu wafer marshmallow carrot cake. Bonbon topping soufflé caramels. Topping sugar plum sesame snaps lollipop wafer carrot cake chocolate. Cake chocolate bar cake sweet. Apple pie brownie macaroon tiramisu tart powder sweet roll bonbon. Gummies biscuit candy canes sugar plum cupcake dragée toffee muffin topping.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 01:44:22', '2017-09-17 19:29:36', '10039a03-adab-435e-8af2-0d6f36a3eb49'),
 ('16', '55', 'en_us', '<p>Cheesecake cupcake lollipop muffin. Cheesecake icing wafer jujubes lollipop muffin sweet chocolate bar dragée. Cake chupa chups chocolate muffin jelly bear claw. Tart jelly toffee pastry cake. Icing ice cream bear claw. Caramels soufflé bonbon chocolate marshmallow. Icing carrot cake jujubes dessert cookie.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 01:44:22', '2017-09-17 19:29:36', 'b4360a6f-b7d5-48ad-b6e7-b9b66a91cfb4'),
 ('17', '64', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-20 01:47:51', '2017-09-17 19:29:36', 'e95b371b-f8e1-4fe3-b4e3-c01cd2aea9c8'),
 ('18', '146', 'en_us', NULL, '“This film brought the house down. I cannot imagine now having done this without it.”', 'Brian Chesky', 'CEO of Airbnb', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"show\"]', '2017-08-30 22:22:29', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', 'fd1caad1-c016-4dc2-aa9d-2f3f07b0a960'),
 ('19', '147', 'en_us', '<h2>The Mission</h2>\n<p>On November 17, 2016, Airbnb announced the largest product expansion in its history. Just five weeks earlier, Bokeh was asked to join its sprint to the finish line.</p>\n<p>Working alongside engineering, brand, product marketing, art, and C-level teams, we developed myriad content to educate users on new features, advertise and build awareness on social media, and, ultimately, to introduce the world to Airbnb Trips on-stage at Airbnb Open in Los Angeles.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:22:29', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', 'e6a84c3b-efcb-4050-be6b-0b7b35d592ab'),
 ('21', '153', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://vimeo.com/193175968', 'Welcome to the World of Trips | Aired During Airbnb Open 2016 Keynote', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '90203f47-8e08-4281-a3b5-d4bc8c975926'),
 ('23', '155', 'en_us', '<h2>Let’s get functional</h2>\n<p>Humanity is a core component of the Airbnb brand. Every feature and service built into the new Airbnb app derives value from the way it connects to guests, hosts, and experiences. To reinforce this connection, we melded organic live-action footage with engaging UI animations and garnished it all with a touch of whimsy. The result was twelve functional product videos viewable in landscape and portrait mode.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '27768f68-29a0-4b9a-8465-fa374eff403d'),
 ('25', '157', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '13670490-8b75-4497-9cae-184eafd6198f'),
 ('26', '162', 'en_us', '<h2>The Reveal</h2>\n<p>With two days before Airbnb Open, Brian needed a Hail Mary. He lacked a centerpiece for the launch announcement that firmly connected Airbnb’s digital product with the human experiences it fosters. So he asked us to apply our creative approach to the keynote anthem and make a film about the future of home sharing.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', 'ae394f81-86c0-4131-9a6e-577349ef6453'),
 ('28', '164', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '6184b88a-6c42-4b92-9889-284274d8b8d2'),
 ('29', '165', 'en_us', '<h2>Marketing Master Blaster</h2>\n<p>To build awareness, we applied this approach to four 15-second advertisements blasted across digital and social channels.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '35f1a283-1e27-424e-8b82-efd24bade08d'),
 ('30', '166', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://vimeo.com/193184792', 'Airbnb Collections Teaser | Aired During AO 2016 Keynote', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '792b8428-a6dc-4e12-aacc-b2b2667b7677'),
 ('31', '167', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:37:36', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '485d0d4e-e8d2-4424-b42e-6ccd7af64f96'),
 ('33', '179', 'en_us', '<h2>The payoff</h2>\n<p>The assets were leveraged across a variety of channels from Airbnb Open to product landing pages, social and YouTube, email newsletters, and paid media. The functional videos amassed over <strong>11 million views in less than three weeks</strong>. On Airbnb product pages, the <strong>video click-through-rate reached as high as 15 percent</strong>. </p>\n<p>We received coverage in the <strong><em>NYTimes</em></strong><strong>, Adweek, </strong><strong><em>Travel + Leisure</em></strong><strong>, TechCrunch, Mashable, </strong><strong><em>The Telegraph</em></strong><strong>, and Fast Company.</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:42:57', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '560e4036-cd0d-487f-bbaa-6abdf3e73e45'),
 ('34', '180', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-08-30 22:42:57', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', 'd1c86bfa-acdc-4a74-b6e3-8007db184881'),
 ('35', '181', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '2017-08-30 22:42:57', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '57e43956-a26f-45c5-846a-588677927cda'),
 ('37', '251', 'en_us', '<h2>Services</h2>\n<ul><li>Concept</li><li>Branding Animation</li><li>Film/Video</li><li>Animation</li><li>Digital Ads</li><li>Social Ads</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-14 00:40:35', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '7150841f-82bb-4947-9659-8b98a3b5cf3c'),
 ('38', '252', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-14 01:28:44', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '75af2c9d-1757-418c-8444-72a2c50658c5'),
 ('39', '281', 'en_us', '<h2>The bow on top</h2>\n<p>Every piece of content featured a reimagined Airbnb motion logo consistent with the fluid design aesthetic we developed for our animations.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-26 01:36:37', '2017-09-26 01:42:55', '24824216-fea5-4407-acaa-cb2dfe1c4a2e'),
 ('40', '282', 'en_us', '<h2>The Mission</h2>\n<p>In May 2016, Instagram asked Bokeh to develop the creative strategy behind its largest business marketing campaign. Over the next six months, Bokeh would trek across four continents and collaborate with twenty-four businesses in eight of Instagram’s top-performing markets to produce eight market-specific anthem films, one global anthem film, and two business profiles.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-26 01:47:21', '2017-09-26 01:48:42', 'd74246e0-e4d6-44b7-821e-2531203656e0'),
 ('41', '283', 'en_us', '<h2>Services</h2>\n<ul><li>Concept</li><li>Branding</li><li>Film/Video</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-26 01:47:21', '2017-09-26 01:48:42', 'dbb9b474-15af-439d-a220-9e3034ba7ef5');
